<s docid="AP900625-0153" num="16" wdcount="6"> Peru, May 31, 1970, 7.7, 66,794.</s>
<s docid="AP900625-0153" num="17" wdcount="6"> Iran, Aug. 31, 1968, 7.4, 12,000.</s>
<s docid="AP900625-0153" num="18" wdcount="6"> Iran, Sept. 1, 1962, 7.1, 12,230.</s>
<s docid="AP900625-0153" num="19" wdcount="6"> Morocco, Feb. 29, 1960, 5.8, 12,000.</s>
