<P>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="29" wdcount="14"> Donations for Iranian earthquake relief are being taken in San Diego by two groups:</s>
</P>
<P>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="30" wdcount="40"> United Nations Fund for the Iran Earthquake (467-1120 or 456-4000) -- Collecting antibiotic and analgesic drugs, collapsible plastic water containers, plastic sheeting, 220-volt portable generators of less than 10 kilowatts, tents, blankets, dry food, light clothing, flashlights and lighting equipment.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="31" wdcount="25"> Bring items or mail checks to 4540 Kearny Villa Road, Suite 214, San Diego 92123; or to 7509 Girard Ave., Suite A, La Jolla 92037.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="32" wdcount="8"> Checks should be made out to the U.N.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="33" wdcount="6"> Fund for the Iran Earthquake .</s>
</P>
