<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="34" wdcount="23"> Southwest Medical Teams (284-7979) -- Through Thursday, collecting sutures, surgical gloves, antibiotics, analgesics (including aspirin), vitamins, ophthalmic solutions and empty blood collection bags.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="35" wdcount="6"> Shipment will be sent July 2.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="36" wdcount="13"> Cash donations will be used to pay to fly the supplies to Iran.</s>
<s docid="LA062390-0001" num="37" wdcount="23"> Mail checks to 3547 Camino del Rio South, Suite C, San Diego 92108, noting that donation is for Iranian Earthquake Relief Fund .</s>
